WEBVTT

00:00:07.282 --> 00:00:08.967
In J.R.R.'s world,

00:00:08.991 --> 00:00:11.977
Gandalf is one of five wizards
sent by the Valar

00:00:12.001 --> 00:00:14.274
to guide the inhabitants of Middle Earth

00:00:14.298 --> 00:00:17.905
in their struggles
against the dark force of Sauron.

00:00:17.929 --> 00:00:19.628
Gandalf's body was mortal,

00:00:19.652 --> 00:00:22.285
subject to the physical
rules of Middle Earth,

00:00:22.309 --> 00:00:24.368
but his spirit was immortal,

00:00:24.392 --> 00:00:26.773
as seen when he died as Gandalf the Grey

00:00:26.797 --> 00:00:29.339
and resurrected as Gandalf the White.

